02/06/84  cu

Syntax:  cu Person_id Project_id


Function: allows the accounting administrator to create a user's home
directory.  Home directories are created automatically when a PDT
containing a new user is installed.  In rare cases, it may be
necessary to execute this function separately.


Arguments:
Person_id
   is the Person_id of the user whose home directory is to be created.
Project_id
   is the Project_id of the project under which the user's home
   directory is created.
